HEADWORD: avaritia
<hw>avaritia</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A reprehensible acquisitiveness;
insatiable desire for wealth (personified as one of the deadly sins);
avarice; greed.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> avarice, greed, covetousness, rapacity</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Avarous</ent>⟦br⟧
